Mystic pizza is the story of three girls - two are sisters and the other is a friend. Daisy is the younger sister and the wildest of the 3. She falls in love but breaks with him after his parents make a racial comment about her. She relates with her sister for the first time because her sister has also recently had a break up with a married man. Daisy ends up getting back together with her ex but unlike in real life it's actually a good decision.